What you need to know:

John Kiplangat, a gold medallst in 1500m in the 2017 Deaflympics in Turkey, and in the 2019 Africa Deaf Championships in Nairobi is one of the athletes who have declared interest in fighting for glory in the upcoming half marathon.“Right now I am doing my best to ensure that I am fit ahead of the competition. The only problem is that there is no camp here (Narok),” said Kiplangat, who was recognised as a hero during this year’s Mashujaa Day celebration held in Kisii.